          },
          "date": "2023-06-16",
          "content": "沒問題的。我們寫英文也有同樣問題。若要假裝中文母語者，建議讓chatGPT幫你順一下\n\"Can you repharse the below sentences as if they are written by a Chinese native speaker?\""
